headline: Northern Trust Joins Project Ensemble to Test the Tokenization of Carbon Credits in a Cross-Border Setting
summary: Under the experimental setting of the HKMA’s Project Ensemble, investors will have access to tokenized voluntary carbon credits traded in Hong Kong via The Northern Trust Carbon Ecosystem™...
